	<h2>Eligibility</h2>
	
	<h3>Registration Interval</h3>
	<p>Registration for both the <a href="#onlinereg">Online Part</a> and <a href="#onsitereg">Onsite Test</a> of PUPC 2015 is <a href="registration.htm" target="_blank">now closed</a>.</p>
	<p>Registration for PUPC 2016 is expected to begin in September 2016.</p>
	<p>Any eligible individual may choose to compete in one or both events, subject to the conditions below. Note that registration for each part is separate.
