	<p>Only individual contestants will be allowed to participate in the PUPC onsite session.</p>
	<p>Individuals must not have been enrolled full-time in a post-secondary institution during the course of the competition (i.e., you are currently a high school student).</p>
	<p>All individuals must be registered to compete.</p>
